{"tid":955192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《環時》替香港01出頭 斥記協「暗中助獨」","createTime":"2018-12-25T08:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T09:00:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"15c452ed1d9e219124d72e86f8952a0b6ae55b4c","tid":955192,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181225/large/1545705670_22ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181225%2Flarge%2F1545705670_22ef.jpg&h=e11bbeee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣搖滾樂隊「閃靈」，不獲工作簽證來港演出。香港01網在採訪公然鼓吹台獨的台灣立委兼「閃靈」成員的林昶佐時，特別加註該網「反對台獨」立場，事後被香港記者協會批評為畫蛇添足。充當中共言論打手的《環球時報》，今日在微博發文，反批記協「暗中助獨」。<br />\n<br />\n《環時》該篇文章以〈「反中」報道不管，香港記協卻對港媒「反台獨」立場零容忍〉為題，指有網民就記協昨日批評香港01網的聲明，作出反駁，指記協對其他「反中」報道從未指正，對香港01網的指責才是「畫蛇添足」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，香港01網本月22日刊登一篇採訪林昶佐的章篇。報道在引述林昶佐對自己的音樂與政治之間的關係時，標註稱「編者按：香港01一貫立場是反對台獨」。記協昨日的聲明稱，媒體不應表明立場，而香港01網的做法「並不尋常，令人憂慮是否因編採人員感到議題敏感，而特別表明立場」。記協表示，記者的責任是將事實呈現，報道並非評論，無需就內容表態。<br />\n<br />\n文章最後又引述一些讀者留言評論指，香港記者協會的做法「證明記協並不反對台獨及港獨」、「實際就是暗中助獨」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181225/59068062\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181225%2F59068062&d=VAjzJnh7VwDGQP9aYpHxP9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=d5b479ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181225%2F59068062&h=8ca518e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181225/59068062</a>"},{"pid":"bfd0223f5ef38fb67c10e4029f0a3b9cd0278675","tid":955192,"uid":35221,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:04:56.000Z","msg":"連狗及其爪牙 x 香港01 x CCTVB x 毒果 x facebook 垃圾專頁 x 共媒<br />\n<br />\n攜手洗腦，令一代香港人冇曬獨立思考"},{"pid":"f299f59c53c11b40b507c6454e4c23b6f117fa60","tid":955192,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:06:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6422b85bbb1ffa0f4116a790a3359b8292a79f1a","tid":955192,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f299f59c53c11b40b507c6454e4c23b6f117fa60","tid":955192,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:06:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:08:17.000Z","msg":"【港航危機】港航明年3月到期債券 收益率飆至191厘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/954147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/954147</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"72097f959555837080d60ce9c2472c2844e8e176","tid":955192,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f299f59c53c11b40b507c6454e4c23b6f117fa60","tid":955192,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:06:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:09:16.000Z","msg":"萬豪信息洩漏指向中國駭客，美國將加大打擊力度<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/939228\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/939228</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0bfbabe50efe745f87f9e8bccc37dc975a4a250a","tid":955192,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f299f59c53c11b40b507c6454e4c23b6f117fa60","tid":955192,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:06:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T08:12:09.000Z","msg":"【好朋友】冷戰升級　習近平恐難招架<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/949959\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/949959</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdd99c55cde43630f3d7531de339b67b555e155","tid":955192,"uid":205462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T09:00:34.000Z","msg":"又要標榜反台獨，又要訪問所謂嘅台獨人士，真係連大契都分唔出你係